misclassification rate on the CIFAR-10 test set. (Error rates have the form µ ± σ, 
where µ is the average over multiple trials and σ is the standard deviation. In PNAS 
we use 15 trials.) "Params" is the number of model parameters. "Cost" is the total 
number of examples processed through SGD (M1E1 + M2E2) before the architecture 
search terminates.
